{
  "id": "61e91b38e9993c001e7e725d",
  "title": "(2.3.1) Task is too big",
  "created": 1548921390,
  "updated": 1553660968,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c1",
      "text": "(2.3.1) Task is too big",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1553660968,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c2",
      "text": "There are people who have only one task but cannot motivate themselvs.",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1553587684,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c3",
      "text": "I asked them whether the task is to finish within 4 hours. 58% of them answered \"no.\" The task is too large, in other words, the goal is too far. We need to [make the goal closer] to keep the motivation.",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921390,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c4",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921390,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c5",
      "text": "Moreover, 75% of those who answer \"no\" do not understand how long the task takes. (*17)",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1553587703,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c6",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1553587694,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c7",
      "text": "They feel as if the task is big because they did not estimate the size of the task. The feeling decreases motivation.",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921390,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c8",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921390,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c9",
      "text": " [(2.3.1.1) Large task of writing a book]",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1553660977,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15ca",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921390,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15cb",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1553587714,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15cc",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553587714,
      "updated": 1553587714,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15cd",
      "text": " Footnote *17:",
      "created": 1548921394,
      "updated": 1553587709,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15ce",
      "text": "\t\tTo be precise, the denominator is A - C below.",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921398,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15cf",
      "text": "\t\tA: People who answered that the task would not end within 4 hours",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921399,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15d0",
      "text": "\t\tB: 52% of A: Those who were able to answer what they do in the first 25 minutes (= small task)",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921402,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15d1",
      "text": "\t\tC: 58% of B: Those who are motivated to do the small task",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921404,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15d2",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548921390,
      "updated": 1548921390,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
